textfsm_template:
Value DOMAIN_ID (\d+)
Value LOCAL_INT (\S+)
Value PEER_ADDRESS (\S+)
Value PEER_LINK (\S+)
Value PEER_LINK_STATUS (up|down)
Value LOCAL_INT_STATUS (up|down)
Value ROLE (\S+)
Value STATE (\S+)
Value SYSTEM_ID (\S+)
Value CONNECTION_STATUS (\S+)

Start
  ^Domain-id\s*:\s*${DOMAIN_ID}
  ^Local-interface\s*:\s*${LOCAL_INT}
  ^Peer-address\s*:\s*${PEER_ADDRESS}
  ^Peer-link\s*:\s*${PEER_LINK}
  ^Peer-link status\s*:\s*${PEER_LINK_STATUS}
  ^Local-Int status\s*:\s*${LOCAL_INT_STATUS}
  ^Role\s*:\s*${ROLE}
  ^State\s*:\s*${STATE}
  ^System-id\s*:\s*${SYSTEM_ID}
  ^Connection status\s*:\s*${CONNECTION_STATUS} -> Record
